# Best Smoke Days — environment variables.
# Copy to .dev.vars for local `wrangler dev`, set via `wrangler secret put`
# for production. None are required for the Step 1 setup; they land as
# later steps wire each integration.

# Sentry — Step 17. Free hobby project DSN.
# SENTRY_DSN=https://...@o0.ingest.sentry.io/0

# MailerLite — Step 6 / Step 11. Tag-segmented subscribers; ~120 req/min
# rate-limit on the free tier — see worker/src/lib/mailerlite/client.ts.
# MAILERLITE_API_KEY=

# Open-Meteo is keyless. NWS requires a contact User-Agent — Step 2.
# NWS_USER_AGENT=pitmaster.tools (contact@pitmaster.tools)
